data.description: Spacious well-maintained turnkey duplex over 1,700 sf situated on the corner of over 5,500 sq ft lot in prime area can have stable rental income. Features 2/1 & 2/1 units; each offering private laundry room, one with brand new central a/c, separate electric & water meters, tankless water heater, fenced yards & 3-4 dedicated parking spaces each. The 2/1 can generate $2,200 monthly & the other 2/1 can be owner occupied. **Do not disturb, drive by only** Conveniently located close to highways, Hardrock Casino & Hotel, airport, parks, schools, & beaches. Exceptional investment opportunity.
